setMarkerBrushLocal 
Game: Armed Assault (1.04) 
Description: Selects the fill texture for the marker ("RECTANGLE" or "ELLIPSE 
"). Brush is the name of the subclass in CfgMarkerBrushes. 
brush can be: "Solid" "Horizontal" "Vertical" "Grid" "FDiagonal" "BDiagonal 
" "DiagGrid" "Cross" "Border" (ArmA2 only) "SolidBorder" (OA only 
)  
Syntax:  
 markerName setMarkerBrushLocal brush 
Parameters: 
markerName: String 
brush: String 
Return Value: 
 Nothing